Name: Office Racer
About the game: Gameplay Office racer is new type of racing game where you race around different levels. You race like a furious head to find the finish lines to beat the game. Its a fun racing game and there is a cool backround music bringing the atmosphere. The car controls from most realistic car driving simulators. You drive with a RC formula car fast as you can win the game. You can meet the old man named Winston in the game. There is a 5 different levels to race. You can find secrets finish lines on the levels. RACE FAST AS YOU CAN! Features RC CAR AMAZING CAR CONTROLS DRIFTING REAL CAR SOUNDS Controls W=GAS S=BRAKE A=LEFT D=RIGHT SPACE=HANDBREAK C=CHANGE CAMERA ANGLE R=RESTART THE LEVEL
